"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20049,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/11\/26\/why-dua-not-answered\/","url_meta":{"origin":34961,"position":1},"title":"Ibrahim on Dua: Why are our supplications not answered?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Qurtubi reported: It was said to Ibrahim ibn Adham, \u201cWhat is wrong with us that we supplicate and receive no answer?\u201d Ibrahim said, \u201cIt is because you know Allah and you do not obey him. You know the Messenger, peace and blessings be upon him, and you do not follow\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27927,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/20\/if-kings-knew\/","url_meta":{"origin":34961,"position":2},"title":"Ibrahim on Islam: If kings knew our inner-peace, they would fight us for it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibrahim ibn Bashar reported: Ibrahim ibn Adham, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf the kings and their sons knew what we experience of pleasure and happiness in Islam, they would fight us for it with their swords.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd al-Kabi\u0304r lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 80 \u0639\u0646 \u0625\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u064a\u0645 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0628\u064e\u0634\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0631\u064d \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0625\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;S